text: Iphinopsis euthymei is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The maximum shell size is 9.5 mm ==Distribution== This species is found along South East Africa. ==References== * Bouchet P. & Warén A. (1985). Revision of the Northeast Atlantic bathyal and abyssal Neogastropoda excluding Turridae (Mollusca, Gastropoda). Bollettino Malacologico Suppl. 1: 121–296 Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1960
title: Iphinopsis euthymei
